\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 For if ye again strengthen yourselves, ye shall again be vanquished.
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid8260773 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 And whatsoever counsel ye shall take, the Lord shall bring it to nought.
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 And the word, whatsoever ye speak, shall not remain with you.
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 And of your fear we shall be neither afraid nor in dread.
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 But the Lord our God, Him will we hallow, and he shall be fear unto us.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 And if I be trusting in Him, He shall be unto me sanctification.
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 And I will be hoping in Him, and shall be saved by Him.
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 Behold I and the children which God hath given me.
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 The people that walk in darkness have seen a great light.
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 Ye that dwell in the region and shadow of death, a light shall shine upon you.
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 For unto us a Child is born, unto us a Son is given.
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 Whose government is upon His shoulder.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 And of His peace there is no end.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 And His name shall be called Angel of Great Counsel.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 Wonderful Counselor.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 Mighty God, Ruler, Prince of Peace.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 Father of the age to come.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 FOR GOD IS WITH US.
\par }{\cs59\b\i\f1\fs28\cf15\insrsid7473308 Choir:}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308  }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 God is with us, understand, O ye nations, and submit yourselves: for God is with us.}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308  }{
\cs44\i\f1\cf6\insrsid7473308 (Twice, if there are two choirs)
\par }{\cs56\i\f1\insrsid7473308 Reader: }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 Glory to the Father, and to the Son, and to the Holy Spirit.
\par }{\cs59\b\i\f1\fs28\cf15\insrsid7473308 Choir:}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308  }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 God is with us}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 .
\par }{\cs56\i\f1\insrsid7473308 Reader: }{\cs55\f1\fs32\insrsid7473308 Both now and ever, and unto the ages of ages. Amen.
\par }{\cs59\b\i\f1\fs28\cf15\insrsid7473308 Choir:}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308  }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 God is with us. For God is with us!
\par }{\cs44\i\f1\cf6\insrsid2229485 
\par }{\cs44\i\f1\cf6\insrsid7473308 And immediately these }{\cs44\i\f1\cf6\insrsid4547475 Troparia}{\cs44\i\f1\cf6\insrsid7473308 : 
\par }{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308 
\par }{\cs59\b\i\f1\fs28\cf15\insrsid7473308 Choir 1:}{\cs53\b\fs36\insrsid7473308  }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 The day being past, I give Thee thanks, O Lord; * the evening, I pray, together with the night * with
out sin grant me, O Savior, * and save me.}{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308\charrsid13855502 
\par }{\cs59\b\i\f1\fs28\cf15\insrsid7473308\charrsid13855502 Choir }{\cs59\b\i\f1\fs28\cf15\insrsid13855502 2: }{\cs58\f1\fs36\cf15\insrsid7473308 Glory to the Father, and to the Son, * and to the Holy Spirit.
